                        <interp inst="t18370227-name-174" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS ENSUM</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an officer. I was with Hagar—I have heard his evidence—it is correct.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
